  "title": "Three large white UFOs over Belo Horizonte [2012]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/04/794/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-cO",
  "content": "<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>APRIL 20th, 2012.</strong> At 11.05 pm, in the southeastern region of the city of Belo Horizonte, State of Minas Gerais, near Serra do Curral, on a night of good visibility, a witness spotted three large white UFOs from his apartment window, with indefinite form and moving at great speed. The three UFOs were at an altitude of approximately 10 km and, according to the report, they left no trace of any kind when traveling. The sighting lasted two seconds.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo &#8216;Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)&#8217;. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.684. &#8220;</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado (ovni) perto da Serra do Curral, Belo Horizonte, Minas Gerais&#8221;. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our &#8216;Info&#8217; page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [&#8220;Código de Referência&#8221;] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
